## (5)(e) Error Detection and Correction

> List two error detection and error correction mechanisms used in wireless communications. *(2 marks)*

---

**Error Detection:**

| Mechanism | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **CRC** | Cyclic Redundancy Check - polynomial division |
| **Parity bits** | Simple odd/even check |

**Error Correction:**

| Mechanism | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Hamming codes** | Block code, corrects single-bit errors |
| **Convolutional codes** | Stream code, uses Viterbi decoding |

